<header>
  <div id="cabecalho">
    <h1 >iNote</h1>
    <figure>
      <a href="">
        <img src="./source/img/entrar.png">
        <figcaption>Entrar</figcaption>
      </a>
    </figure>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="d-flex flex-column w-100">
<div class="btn-group mx-auto">
  <button type="button" class="add btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
  <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Nova Anotação...
  </button>
    <div class="dropdown-menu">
      <form class="col-md-6" action="/" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control-lg" id="exampleDropdownFormEmail1" placeholder="Título">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="text" name="content" class="form-control-lg" id="exampleDropdownFormPassword1" placeholder="Conteúdo">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Salvar</button>
      </form>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="cardNote" class="d-flex flex-wrap m-5">
  <div class="card text-white bg-dark mb-3 mr-3 ml-3 mt-3 mb-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
    <div class="card-header">
      <button class="edit">
        <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
      </button>
      <button class="delete">
        <i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body text-light">
      <h5 class="card-title">Título de Card Dark</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Um exemplo de texto rápido para construir o título do card e fazer preencher o conteúdo do card.</p>
      <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Atualizados 3 minutos atrás</small></p>
    </div>
</div>